  "texts": [
    "Rather than focusing solely on the creation of new digital products or services, digital business innovators should instead focus on the strategic application of digital technologies to improve and reinvent existing business models.",
    "Physical assets and labor-intensive procedures are cornerstones of many established business models and value propositions.",
    "However, digital business models and value propositions use digital technologies to offer novel approaches to value creation and delivery.",
    "Small and medium-sized enterprises (SMEs) that want to innovate their businesses in the digital realm need to have a firm grasp on the capabilities made available by digital technologies and a thorough comprehension of customer needs and behavior.",
    "According to Venkatesh et al.'s (2020) study of Indian SMEs, the size of the company and its focus on a particular market segment has a major impact on the company's ability to innovate."
  ],
